## Oauth Authorization Code [/api.factory.zone/v1/oauth/authorization_code]

When using the "authorization code" grant type for Oauth Authentication, 
we uses this resource to fetch the authorization code.


### Retrieve Authorization code [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "clientId": "9djnjfkslsldtrsjyefomncv",
            "responseType": "code",
            "callbackUrl": "http://whereithappens.com",
            "scope": "ReadWrite"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)
        
        {
            "callbackurl": "http://whereithappens.com/#auth_code=87sgsshjshkaj57sjxgxg"
        }
        

## Oauth Access Token [/api.factory.zone/v1/oauth/access_token]

(Grant Type - Authorization Code)
When using the "Authorization Code" grant type, we use this resource to request for access token

### Request Access Token [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "clientId": "0hdbdvwhaswryuijgsjasdbs",
            "clientSecret": "6cbcbcnmsnnssmsssert",
            "authCode": "87sgsshjshkaj57sjxgxg",
            "callbackUrl": "http://bentotech.com/",
            "scope": "read"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "accessToken": "4aschdbdsmlxkuctsgsjskckcmcm",
            "tokenType": "bearer",
            "expiresIn": "21500",
            "refreshToken": "7liusigsloufhhfgvgcbbnjj",
            "scope": "read",
            "userId": "jd3h45vvnvjhdurt7rhru3",
            "info": {
                "firstName": "Chris",
                "lastName": "Soyborg",
                "email": "soyborg@mail.com"
            }
        }
        
        
## Oauth Access Token [/api.factory.zone/v1/oauth/authorize]

(Grant Type - Implicit)
When using the "Implicit" grant type, we use this resource to request an access token.
This grant type does not support refresh tokens.

### Request Access Token [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "clientId": "0hdbdvwhaswryuijgsjasdbs",
            "responseType": "token",
            "callbackUrl": "http://bentotech.com/",
            "scope": "read"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "callbackUrl": "http://bentotech.com/#token=6jutbdhcbvbvnvjsbxxnxnx"
        }